{
  "stem": "18770.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 322.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Roosevelt is going to be the great, white father, whatever it is, you know, who, who maybe can help us, or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's-- that-- I hear the name mentioned.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We have some distant relatives in Canada.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We get to Canada.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We don't have the clothes for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember my mother goes to a-- something probably like ORT, you know, one of those Jewish committees set up for refugees, and gets me some-- what I'm wearing are short pants with stockings-- wool stockings, which is very humiliating for a boy, you know.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, that's not the way the kids are dressing in school in Canada.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because I'm put in a school there when we get there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so she gets me the pants that boys wear in Canada, which were like jodhpurs at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And but we first, first-- that's when we went to Toronto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First, we get to Vancouver.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stay there for the first-- for about a month or two.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "First time I've ever seen an English movie-- a movie in English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't understand a word of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's like a dream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I walk in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I watched this movie.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you have to try to figure out what it is, right?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My aunt-- one of my aunts is from England, Jewish but from England.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so on the boat over, she has taught us 10 words, [LAUGHS] you know what I'm saying, that kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're put immediately into schools.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, there are no classes for refugee kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I don't speak any English, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
